snippet.title: Planet Coaster: Console Edition | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Planet Coaster, the best PC coaster sim of all time, is coming to PlayStation 4 and PlayStation 5, as well as Xbox One and Xbox Series X!

Build and manage your way to coaster-creating fame! Deep physics-based systems mean you're in for the ride of your life, so dream big and build even bigger as you create your theme park empire.

Planet Coaster: Console Edition is coming Holiday 2020.


For more news and information about Planet Coaster:

Website: https://planetcoaster.com/ 
Forums: https://forums.planetcoaster.com/ 
Facebook: https://facebook.com/PlanetCoaster 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlanetCoaster 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/planetcoaster/
